race.comment: WHOLELOTTALOVE (6) started at $3.50 last time and ran below expectations, finishing ninth and beaten 11 lengths at Winton over 1200m. Is much better than that and on his best form he is one of the chief contenders. VIKING VALOUR (3) lines up on the back of a 3.5 lengths fourth over 1000m at Cloncurry. Well placed and should be tough to beat. HELLARAMA (7) tasted defeat last start when eighth over 1000m at Cloncurry. Placed to advantage so expect a better run. HI ZERO (2) finished eighth at this track and distance at his last appearance five-and-a-half months ago. Among the better hopes while fresh.
